Build a Canvas App in Power Apps connected to Dataverse to manage 
the Well Assurance process for an Oil & Gas company.

The following Dataverse tables already exist in this environment, 
do NOT create new tables, connect directly to them:
- coepp_pronostico
- coepp_pronostico_detalles
- coepp_casos
- coepp_casos_detalles

--- ROLES (Azure AD Groups) ---
- Reservoir
- Assurance
- Production Engineering
- Management Control (CdG)
- P&L / Programming
- YAD / Geology / Others (read-only)

--- KEY BUSINESS RULES ---
1. Only one case in Draft or Open status per Child PAD at a time.
2. To create Case 3: all previous cases for that PAD must be Closed or Cancelled.
3. If latest case is Closed → next case is Case 2.
4. If latest case is Cancelled → new Case 3 can be created.
5. On status change to Open: Parent Wells set is frozen (no add or delete).
6. Structural fields become read-only for all roles when case is Open.
7. Assurance can edit any field as contingency, but Justification is always mandatory.
8. Closing Case 3 → system automatically creates Case 2 for the same Child PAD.
9. Maxima_Presion_Esperada is always calculated, never editable.
10. CdG can only fill Orden_Interna_Nro if Tipo_Aseguramiento = AB or AD.
11. If Pozo_Padre_Origen = Manual → Justification mandatory on creation.
12. If Carga_Manual_Whpi_Ind = YES → Presion_Inicial editable for Reservoir in Draft.

--- SCREENS NEEDED ---
1. Active Forecast - Child PADs list
2. Cases list for a selected Child PAD
3. Case detail with status management and Parent Wells gallery
4. Parent Well form with role-based field permissions

